data.description: Welcome to this exquisite two-story home in Brickhope Plantation, where modern elegance meets Southern charm. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence features a harmonious open floor plan, high ceilings, and gleaming wood flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere for both living and entertaining.Highlights of this home include:A versatile office space and formal dining room on the main level.A gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a center island, and ample storage.A luxurious master suite with a spa-like ensuite, featuring a soaking tub and separate shower.A loft-style bonus room, offering flexibility for additional living space or a bedroom.A serene fenced backyard with wooded views and access to community pool amenities. As you step inside, the high, smooth ceilings and rich wood flooring guide you through the open-concept first floor, from the roomy office/living space to the elegant dining area. The heart of the home, the expansive kitchen, is a chef's delight and perfect for hosting, flowing seamlessly into the main living area with its white columns and pendant lighting.  Upstairs, the bedrooms are generously sized, each with carpeting, ceiling fans, and ample closet space. The master bedroom, a peaceful retreat, includes a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite. The second-floor laundry adds convenience to everyday living.  Outside, the spacious backyard offers a peaceful setting for relaxation and outdoor activities.  Excitingly, the seller is offering $7,000 in credits to help buy down the buyer's interest rate or go towards home updates with an acceptable offer. Additionally, the home features an assumable VA loan from 2020, providing a unique financing opportunity.  Don't miss this chance to own a piece of Lowcountry paradise in Brickhope Plantation. Schedule your viewing today!
